task.summary: get a demo react app started (simple search application with github web api) with the initial components and a simple helper class for making requests

- `RemoteCallTransport` can now retrieve repositories from GitHub, with or without an accompanying username - add a component `ChangeSearch` for toggling between user and repository search - refactor `Search` component to be stateless, as well as support searching for repositories - `SearchContainer` is now the sole provider of state through the application, add new properties for maintaining the search input values as well as caching previous search results
